title: Dolphin Gamecube Wii Emulator 4.03 Windows Linux Mac OSX
description:
Please visit https://dolphin-emu.org/ for news, information, install instructions, updates, and compatibility information.


Dolphin is an emulator for two recent Nintendo video game consoles: the GameCube and the Wii. It allows PC gamers to enjoy games for these two consoles in full HD (1080p) with several enhancements: compatibility with all PC controllers, turbo speed, networked multiplayer, and even more!

This Torrent includes the latest optimized development version for Windows x64, Linux/Ubuntu, and MacOS X, as well as the latest stable Windows x86 version, as of 9/30/2014. Please visit the website for newer updates as dev builds are released very often!
